                                                    Sort sort)
        This methods performs tags referencing to real time.
        Parameters:
        tts - measured unreferenced tags
        t0set - t0 time
        baseSeconds - base seconds has to be set for long measurements (>100seconds) to prevent loss of resolution (double precision floating point has 15 digits range)
        errorCorrection - error correction value calculated from 1pps tag measured on ARM input
        sort - sorting order of referenced tags list
